Tchéky Karyo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tch%C3%A9ky_Karyo 0 Tchéky Karyo (French: [tʃeki kɑʁjo]; born 4 October 1953) is a Turkish-born French actor and musician. Beginning his career as an actor on stage in classical and contemporary works, he began to work as a character actor in films in the 1980s. He has acted in numerous films by Hollywood and French directors, including Luc Besson. Tchéky_Karyo ( French : [_tʃeki_kɑʁjo_] ; born_4_October_1953 ) is a_Turkish-born_French_actor_and_musician .
